**Replace with:** `bp6-`

```bash
grep -n "bp[45]-" docs/MMS_COMPLETE_SPECIFICATION.md
```

---

### Task 4.3: Update Design Tokens Format (Section 8)

**Old format:**
```json
{
  "color-primary": "#1d4ed8"
}
```

**New format (W3C 2025.10):**
```json
{
  "color": {
    "primary": {
      "$type": "color",
      "$value": "#1d4ed8",
      "$description": "Primary brand color"
    }
  }
}
```

---

## Verification Checklist

After all updates:

- [ ] No `@zazcart/toolkit` references remain
- [ ] All state examples use @belt/tools API
- [ ] ECM section exists in Chapter 2
- [ ] RAMS section exists in Chapter 2
- [ ] BRIN index documented in Section 19
- [ ] OR-Tools timeout configured in Section 20
- [ ] Demo fallback documented in Chapter 25
- [ ] Blueprint.js uses `bp6-` prefix
- [ ] Design tokens use W3C 2025.10 format
- [ ] Document compiles without errors

---

## Commit Strategy

After each session:

```bash
git add docs/MMS_COMPLETE_SPECIFICATION.md
git commit -m "$(cat <<'EOF'
docs(spec): [SESSION_N] update MMS specification

- [List of changes]

Based on Gemini review evaluation (2026-01-05)
Migrated from @zazcart/toolkit to @belt/tools@0.0.1

🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
EOF
)"
```

